stateDiagram-v2

    [] --> Created

    Created --> Assigned : AssignCase

    Assigned --> Investigating : StartInvestigation

    Investigating --> AwaitingApproval : SubmitRecommendation
    Investigating --> Closed : CloseCase

    AwaitingApproval --> Approved : ApproveCase
    AwaitingApproval --> Rejected : RejectCase

    Rejected --> Investigating : ReopenCase
    Rejected --> Closed : CloseCase

    Approved --> ExecutingAction : ExecuteAction

    ExecutingAction --> Closed : ActionCompleted

    Closed --> []

    note right of Created
      AssignCase
      Actor: FraudAnalyst
    end note

    note right of AwaitingApproval
      ApproveCase / RejectCase
      Actor: GovernanceOfficer
    end note

    note right of ExecutingAction
      ExecuteAction
      Actor: System
    end note
